olar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Al-Khaffaf B, Knox F, Bundred NJ. Idiopathic granulomatous mastitis: a 25-year experience. <em>J Am Coll Surg</em> 2008;206(2):269–273.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jamcollsurg.2007.07.041">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18222379/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Idiopathic+granulomatous+mastitis%3A+a+25-year+experience&amp;author=B+Al-Khaffaf&amp;author=F+Knox&amp;author=NJ+Bundred&amp;publication_year=2008&amp;journal=J+Am+Coll+Surg&amp;pages=269-273&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.jamcollsurg.2007.07.041&amp;pmid=18222379">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Altintoprak F, Karakece E, Kivilcim T, et al. Idiopathic granulomatous mastitis: an autoimmune disease? <em>Sci World J</em> 2013;2013:148727.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1155/2013/148727">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Idiopathic+granulomatous+mastitis%3A+an+autoimmune+disease%3F&amp;author=F+Altintoprak&amp;author=E+Karakece&amp;author=T+Kivilcim&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;journal=Sci+World+J&amp;pages=148727&amp;doi=10.1155%2F2013%2F148727">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">8.</div><div id="r8" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Bani-Hani KE, Yaghan RJ, Matalka II, Shatnawi NJ. Idiopathic granulomatous mastitis: time t